title: Went to sleep...
body: So last night I was on a streak, had two wins down on promo's and was like tomorrow ill win my last match to get into gold. So I woke up and played a match, after 40ish minutes I was victorious then BAM 1/10... FOK WUT IS DIS

replies.body: Moral of the story; don't sleep, only League. {{champion:39}}
You are lucky, great way to start season 5.
